{"id":108068,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/简讯：日首相表明不会向中国道歉/","date":"2010-09-26T16:11:59Z","modified":"2010-09-27T04:32:26Z","title":"简讯：日首相表明不会向中国道歉","content":"<div>\n<p>日本首相菅直人表明，日本不会就钓鱼岛（日本称尖阁诸岛）撞船事件向中国作出道歉。</p>\n<p>菅直人说：“尖阁诸岛是日本固有领土。无法考虑道歉和赔偿。我完全没有进行回应的打算。”</p>\n<p>菅直人的讲话是在过去一天以来，日方就中方索赔要求的最高级回应。</p>\n<p>中国外交部发言人姜瑜此前重申，中方“有权要求日方作出道歉和赔偿”。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/fictf1hqJhs__nTj6VRdV0QEzTk/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/fictf1hqJhs__nTj6VRdV0QEzTk/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/fictf1hqJhs__nTj6VRdV0QEzTk/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/fictf1hqJhs__nTj6VRdV0QEzTk/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=h0OHOjMbmXI:kz2MvbZElUc:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=h0OHOjMbmXI:kz2MvbZElUc:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=h0OHOjMbmXI:kz2MvbZElUc:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=h0OHOjMbmXI:kz2MvbZElUc:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=h0OHOjMbmXI:kz2MvbZElUc:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=h0OHOjMbmXI:kz2MvbZElUc:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/h0OHOjMbmXI\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.